ub.com/ftlabs/fastclick\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><strong>fastclick</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><strong>date-fns</strong></a> - 时间处理。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"数据流\"><a href=\"#%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E6%B5%81\" aria-label=\"数据流 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>数据流</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/reduxjs/redux\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><strong>redux</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/mweststrate/immer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><strong>immer</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/mobxjs/mobx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><strong>mobx</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/jamiebuilds/unstated\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><strong>unstated</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/ReactiveX/rxjs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><strong>rxjs</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/dvajs/dva\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><strong>dva</strong></a> - 我写的数据流，基于 redux。</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rematch/rematch\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><strong>rematch</strong></a> - 基于 redux。</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/vuejs/vuex\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><strong>v